{
  "title": "Indulgent Middle Eastern Mozzarella Bowl",
  "description": "A rich, cheese-pulled bowl with a sweet mirin-hon glaze, wrapped in parchment for a moist finish. It’s a quick, gluten-free dish bursting with Middle Eastern spices.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
  "diet": [
